{"key": "qm5_round1", "rev": 2, "text": " Let us trigger the practice by making a long exhalation, exhale from the nose, from the chest from the belly and empty yourself of air. Allow the body to inhale freely onto the body of empty of air. Exhale again from the nose, from the chest, from the belly. Focus on exhalation in a vertical top down from the top, from the chest. Just pull the belly in to push out the air, inhale as your body desires, shallow or deep. Keep your attention on exhalation. from the nose, from the chest, from the belly. With the next exhalation, bring your attention to your chest area And with each exhale, bring your mind lower towards the abdominal area. Exhale from the top, from the chest, and as you exhale from the belly, Bring your mind towards the center of gravity. Use the exhalation to help your mind lower towards the belly. on the next exhale down connect with your center of gravity Pull the belly in, push out the air and stay in the center of gravity. Thank you.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 3.660000000000002, "end": 18.86, "text": " Let us trigger the practice by making a long exhalation, exhale from the nose, from the", "tokens": [50364, 961, 505, 7875, 264, 3124, 538, 1455, 257, 938, 454, 4947, 399, 11, 19652, 490, 264, 6690, 11, 490, 264, 51306], "temperature": 0, "avg_logprob": -0.22029300530751547, "compression_ratio": 1.144736842105263, "no_speech_prob": 0.04295544698834419, "words": [{"word": " Let", "start": 3.660000000000002, "end": 4.56, "probability": 0.6385921835899353}, {"word": " us", "start": 4.56, "end": 4.78, "probability": 0.9935959577560425}, {"word": " trigger", "start": 4.78, "end": 5.14, "probability": 0.9955001473426819}, {"word": " the", "start": 5.14, "end": 5.34, "probability": 0.9882871508598328}, {"word": " practice", "start": 5.34, "end": 5.8, "probability": 0.9822458028793335}, {"word": " by", "start": 5.8, "end": 7.28, "probability": 0.9649240970611572}, {"word": " making", "start": 7.28, "e